<h1>Audit (A-03-13-00029)</h1>

<h2>02-11-2014<br />
Palmetto Health Baptist Hospital Incorrectly Billed Medicare Inpatient Claims With Kwashiorkor</h2>

<h2 class="line">Complete Report</h2>

